# Keep latest-per-env and quarterly snapshots tracked; ignore everything else.
# Intermediate runs stay local, per the Phase 2 evidence-retention policy
# (docs/plans/2026-04-25-002-feat-capacity-release-gates-and-telemetry-plan.md).
#
# U4 note: `local-worker-stdout.log` is produced by the capacity-local-worker
# orchestrator (redacted wrangler stdout/stderr) and is covered by the `*`
# rule below. Never commit it; it is scrubbed but still operator-facing log.
#
# P4-U11: certifiable cert-run evidence lives under `evidence/` and is
# tracked alongside the capacity.md row that cites it; verify-capacity-evidence
# fails on a row whose evidence path does not exist on disk.
*
!.gitignore
!latest-*.json
!snapshots/
!snapshots/**
!configs/
!configs/**
!evidence/
!evidence/**
# P3 telemetry gate: raw Worker/Tail captures stay local because they can
# contain unrelated live traffic or request metadata. Commit only redacted
# `*-tail-correlation.json`, `*-statement-map.json`, classification, and
# capacity evidence artefacts.
evidence/**/*worker-log*.json
evidence/**/*worker-log*.jsonl
evidence/**/*worker-log*.ndjson
evidence/**/*worker-log*.log
evidence/**/*worker-log*.txt
evidence/**/*pretty-tail*.json
evidence/**/*pretty-tail*.jsonl
evidence/**/*pretty-tail*.ndjson
evidence/**/*pretty-tail*.log
evidence/**/*pretty-tail*.txt
evidence/**/*raw-tail*.json
evidence/**/*raw-tail*.jsonl
evidence/**/*raw-tail*.ndjson
evidence/**/*raw-tail*.log
evidence/**/*raw-tail*.txt
evidence/**/*tail-raw*.json
evidence/**/*tail-raw*.jsonl
evidence/**/*tail-raw*.ndjson
evidence/**/*tail-raw*.log
evidence/**/*tail-raw*.txt
!README.md
